00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:11,740
parallel to the surface,

139
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:15,600
little protractors which also lie in the surface,

140
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:19,340
and can do geometry on the surface without ever

141
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:23,080
pointing their ruler or their protractor out of the surface.

142
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:29,400
That's the term that comes up is intrinsic.

143
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:30,820
In other words,

144
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:33,320
