00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,740
and those are called extrinsic.

148
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,380
Intrinsic and extrinsic.

149
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:46,820
We are now interested only in

150
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:50,220
the intrinsic properties that this very,

151
00:05:50,220 --> 00:05:52,340
very small bug would discover.

152
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,080
Right.

153
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:57,800
By doing experimental geometry on the surface with

154
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:02,500
tools that can only lie in the surface.

155
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:03,580
Okay.

156
00:06:03,740 --> 00:06:04,580
All right.

157
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:07,050
So we're talking about the

158
00:06:07,050 --> 00:06:09,480
