159
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:14,280
and the idea of parallel transport is an intrinsic idea.

160
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:16,820
If that little bug had wheels,

161
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:20,780
think of a little bug with little wheels.

162
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,120
Little dumbbell shaped affair.

163
00:06:26,380 --> 00:06:31,160
Two wheels that could roll on the surface.

164
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:34,160
If the wheels had exactly the same size,

165
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,840
and they couldn't,

166
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:37,790
and of course I'm assuming that

167
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:39,740
they cannot rotate relative to each other,

168
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:42,360
then if I rolled it along the tabletop here,

169
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,100
it would describe a straight arc,

