2038
01:20:13,914 --> 01:20:15,974
The real notion of charge conservation

2039
01:20:15,974 --> 01:20:18,494
is what's called local charge conservation.

2040
01:20:18,754 --> 01:20:20,774
It doesn't mean that the amount of charge

2041
01:20:20,774 --> 01:20:22,114
