2042
01:20:22,114 --> 01:20:24,434
It means that any change

2043
01:20:24,434 --> 01:20:26,754
in the charge in the room

2044
01:20:26,754 --> 01:20:31,714
is due to observable flows of charge through the walls.

2045
01:20:32,034 --> 01:20:34,594
The only way the charge can change in the room

2046
01:20:35,084 --> 01:20:37,954
is if it flows through the walls.

2047
01:20:38,314 --> 01:20:40,174
So an increase in charge

2048
01:20:40,174 --> 01:20:42,634
